title: Shaya Cottage
description: >-
  Located in Sekotong, 50 km from Meru Temple, SHAYA cottage features
  accommodation with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a garden
  and a terrace. Among the facilities at this property are room service and
  luggage storage space, along with free WiFi throughout the property. You can
  enjoy French and Indonesian dishes at the restaurant or have a cocktail at the
  bar.
